Class WeatherStationDailyEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.WeatherStationDailyEntry

  • public class WeatherStationDailyEntry
extends java.lang.Object
    Weather Stations store an entry for each day of the month with data related to the climate on that particular day. TODO: Getters for data. TODO: Decide how to store Time for time variable.
